::Perndabot::

Perndabot sees Antagony up ahead and swoops down, landing near her and
keeping his weapons ready.

"I am Perndabot, Alliance member," he says as introduction, "Are you
hostile or friendly?"

If she was hostile, he didn't expect a friendly responce.
